Author: gartmah
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: Taylor is not a company of a single app. We are actually a lot more than that!  Taylor’s mission is to bring cryptocurrency to everyone, our smart trading assistant app and the Taylor Crypto Academy are our initial approach to it. However, our efforts won’t end there.  The Taylor Trading Assistant app and the Taylor Crypto Academy are our first efforts to achieve our goal to bring cryptocurrency trading to the masses. But we want to do more, and the nature of our company allows us that. We will look into other possibilities and study their feasibility for the future. Our goal is to add extra value to the Taylor subscription plans, as well as to the TAY token itself. It’s important to note that these are ideas and not promises. Our intention with this article is to be transparent, and let out community know some potential ideas related to our service/company that we would like to consider once our initial milestones are achieved.  We would like to investigate in the future the possible implementation of features such as trailing stops and high-frequency trading (HTF) and the creation of services such as exchange-to-exchange arbitrage, ICO reviews and recommendation, and maybe a lab/incubator for entrepreneurs who may want to create solutions that are aligned with our mission. And much more.  Again these are only ideas that we believe to be cohesive with our business model. As new possibilities for the Taylor service/app and company as a whole become feasible, we will start planning their implementation and begin announcing their time frame. For now, this is what our community can expect from us in the upcoming months:  . The Taylor app . The Taylor Crypto Academy . Follow us and stay in touch  https://medium.com/smarttaylor/taylor-is-not-a-company-of-a-single-app-we-are-actually-a-lot-more-than-that-2c959174365c

Body: The beta version will be free for everyone! We're launching it in the upcoming weeks.  Sign up to try the beta here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1p0KafEOUYh8bF-fzokjf9_kRENmG4BroEENpSciL3Tc/viewform  The first version of the app after (after the beta) will be free to try, with a maximum number of trades allowed. The standard plan will be free for users who hold at least 1000 TAY for as long as they hold it. The premium plan will be free for users who hold at least 3000 TAY for as long as they hold it.

Author: butlimous
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: Hi  Here the answers to your questions:  1) Initially, the beta and the final app will support Bittrex. After that, Binance and the other major ones would be their next target. The trading pairs will simply be all those found in the exchange so Altcoins are included. Actually BTC/USD can NOT be traded directly. Currently there are no fiat/crypto direct exchanges at least the well known ones do not support it. In the future, they have a plan to pool multiple exchanges together like if you have balances in both Bittrex and Binance, you can hook both up into the app and get signals from both!  2) I advise you to read their whitepaper to get the answer for this question and others and to understand how it works: https://smarttaylor.io/static/documents/taylor-whitepaper.pdf  You are right. Taylor is simply different from all other projects out there but they don't have that much buzz other products is getting. Make sure as well to get into the Telegram channel to get quicker answers for any questions you have.  Thanks Regards Michael

Author: MihailJ
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: IMPORTANT ANNOUNCEMENT! Taylor’s token sale has been postponed for 48 hours.  In order to provide a fair experience to our investors, we decided to postpone the crowd sale launch time in a few hours. A few hours before the token sale, due to a technical issue in one of our server-side systems, some investors experienced a delay in our website while submitting their Ether wallet address to be whitelisted in the token sale smart contract in the Ethereum blockchain.  To guarantee that all investors have the same and fast experience that is needed to be fair in a first come, first serve basis, we decided to postpone the token sale for 48h, time enough to update the server-side system and website and thoroughly test the fix which has already been addressed.  The new time of the token sale launch is February 21 at 2 PM UTC. The end date is now March 22 at 11:59 PM UTC.  We understand that this decision may be bothersome but, as we have mentioned before, we want to have a glitch-free token sale and be fair to all investors.  We kindly thank you for your support and wish you a great token sale participation!  https://medium.com/smarttaylor/important-announcement-taylors-token-sale-has-been-postponed-for-48-hours-7ba3a1b88242

Author: fseixas
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: The best way to understand our service and app is to watch our introductory video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kmNlO-MtoiQ  Here is an explanation: Our market monitor bot watch for trading opportunities in hundreds of coin pairs. Once found, it will notify users through the mobile app. Users will then decide if they want to enter that trade using the funds they have in their exchanges. Author: debaas
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: I have been following this project for some time and really itching to invest in the token sale. The updated whitepaper where it says you get basic app access for 1000 TAY is nice and i will probably use that.  The thing i just don't see yet is the use of the tokens if you are not planning on using the app.  They say you can pay for a subscription using tokens but you can also do that by credit card, so no real need to buy tokens to get a subscription. The other premium services for which you can pay with TAY are still not clear, so right now i have no clue if these tokens are of any use??  Please explain the use of tokens a bit more. Just can't see the value of it right now if i can also pay for a subscription and additional features with a credit card.  Also if i do the math correctly, 1000 TAY will give you free App access, the basic membership will be around $ 60 a month, so that's $720 a year. So basically 1000 tokens are worth $ 720  (if you considder holding them a year)  which means $ 0,72 cents. The token sale lists 1 TAY at 0,0007 ETH which is around $ 0,63 cents now.  So by taking a risk and buying 1000 TAY i will have to use the app for at least 10 months to end up saving money on a subscription. I might not like it or use it longer than 10 months. Also the first 6 months are free so basically i have to wait 16 months before my ICO tokens will be cheaper than just buying a regular subscription with credit card.   So it comes down to the question: What can i do with the tokens besides using it on TAY services and subscriptions, and what will the exac pricing be of the different subscriptions and additional features.

Author: fseixas
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: debass, thanks for your time analyzing our project.  the use of the token is basically to pay for the service, but sure not only that in the future. There is one feature in our roadmap, the social trading will probably use our tokens to monetize strategies created by our users which is another utility for the token. But for now, it is only to pay for the service. The premium plan will only be accessible for the ones how paid using TAY or by holding 3000 TAY. There is no other way to access the premium plan, even by credit card. So all the value depends on the value of the features in the premium plan. We have many ideas for that, but here are two features that we will implement: 1) higher trading limits Due to the fact that our main user target is newbies to crypto, we will set a strict trading limit for the basic plan. So, every more experienced user will probably want the premium plan which only can be purchased using TAY. 2) priority notifications Since trading opportunities using the scalping strategy have a very short life-span, the users that act quickly will be able to make more profitable trades. We will not delay notification to basic users, but premium users will receive it first.  We believe that only these two features plus more to come will set a proper value on the premium plan.  You said: Quote Also if i do the math correctly, 1000 TAY will give you free App access, the basic membership will be around $ 60 a month, so that's $720 a year. So basically 1000 tokens are worth $ 720  (if you considder holding them a year)  which means $ 0,72 cents. The token sale lists 1 TAY at 0,0007 ETH which is around $ 0,63 cents now.  I think this is not a great comparison since you are comparing the value of one year of holding with an immediate value of the token. The point here is how much 1000 TAY will be valued in one year. Will it be more or less than $720?  Our view of the holding feature is that someone wants to hold because he or she believes that the price will appreciate over time and, because he or she is holding, he or she will be benefited with the free use of the app. That's another way of seeing it.  Another way to see it is the fact that the money you put paying for the subscription is a sunk cost while the holding is not. By holding you can get your money back (or at least part of it depending on the TAY price). I don't think it is fair to compare a sunk cost with money put in holding of tokens.  One information that I need to correct in your thinking is that the first 6 months will be free. That is not correct. The service will be free while the app is still in beta. We will start charging when it leaves the beta.  Thanks again!

Author: crypto_tricky
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: Hi there!  I just created my account here, well, for one thing because I'm new to crypto-currency and really want to educate myself, for second because I stumbled upon your short youtube video "Quick trade, 1% profit in 2 minutes!" when I was reading up on trading strategies and scalping, which eventually brought me here.  So I've been looking at your different web pages, blogs and stuff. I like that you seem quite transparent about what you're doing (but this is only a subjective impression since I'm a total n00b so my judgment is pretty much uneducated), you're keen on giving loads of information on your development team, implementing KYC is probably a sign that you're serious about what you're doing. Heck, even reading you here using the expression "gender non-binary" makes me like you.  But then I get to the point when I keep reading that your project is aimed at dumbing things down to people like me and providing us a tool that can help us with trading, but then it all becomes super complicated with this whole token thing and ICOs (most are scams) and I still haven't figured out what the heck is all this and how do I get in, and what will it cost me... and what exactly will it allow me to do and how reliable it is.  So between all the different platforms you use to communicate, the blogs, the twitters, telegram (which i have no clue how to use yet) I find all of this really confusing and very pretty, but very obscure. Ya get me?   Or, maybe, I'm just being super clueless and thick and I just didn't look in the right places. Be it as it may, your project is aimed at thick and dumb people like me... so there's that.  So would it be possible to ELI5 how to get in SmartTaylor and what to expect from it and what the cost is? THANK YOU!!!

Author: smarttaylor
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: Hi, Crypto_Tricky  Yea, we totally get you! It's too much new info around this cryptoworld. So, first things first: We're launching an app to help people trade cryptocurrencies, and that's our product. We're also issuing our own cryptocurrency - TAY. How? Through a token sale. The token is basically a form of funding for a company and people generally buy coins on token sales because they believe in the project and want to support it and/or believe the coin will appreciate in value over time. For Taylor, those who buy TAY will be able to pay our monthly fee in TAY rather than in fiat currency, and thus have nice discounts and access to exclusive features and benefits. If want to use our app, you just need to wait a little bit until it's launched, but if you also want to participate in our token sale, just go to our website to read more and also sign up to our whitelist wwww.smarttaylor.io  1 Tay will be $0.73 in the first week and will gradually increase in price until the fourth week, as our token sale will last for one month or less if the tokens are sold fast. Minimum buy is only 0.01 ETH, or ~8 dollars as of now Maximum is 50 ETH.  If you have any other questions do not hesitate to reach out to us

Author: crypto_tricky
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: Hi, thx for getting back to me so fast and for your kind answers!    So are you saying that after your token sale (that's about to happen soon) nobody will ever be able to buy TAY anymore?    Also, when will the app be available? Will using Taylor without participating in your ICO also require KYC?  And lastly, what will the monthly fee be, in fiat (or ETH)? Hard to evaluate the benefit of having TAY to pay for it if I have no idea of its value compared to fiat (or ETH). I'm guessing my main interest in TAY would be to pay for Taylor with a discount, not to hodl or trade it as being a baby crypto enthusiast I won't enter any ICOs whatsoever.  Sorry again for the dumb questions.

Author: smarttaylor
Title: [ANN][TAY] Taylor - Smart Crypto Trading Assistant | ICO | Token Sale
Body: Your premise is incorrect, SuperNovah. The learning curve to become an experienced trader is high, and many people either have technical difficulties or a hard time identifying good trade opportunities, or both. That's where we come in, providing smart signals based on advanced technical analysis, AI and sentiment analysis as well as a trading assistant bot that will automatically enter trades for you with stop-loss and stop-gain orders (initially at 1% to 3% in scalping), which allows you to focus on more important/urgent and profitable tasks of yours. Initially, our platform will be more suitable for beginners, but we already have on our roadmap plans of adding complex and personalized features for professional traders as well!
